Description: This package allow you to run your apps at BOINC server. This software consist of 3 parts. The server part must be installed at BOINC server before using this package. You must also build your custom virtual machine with R and install vm part at this machine. Virtual machine is a part of BOINC application, therefore you must download it to your BOINC server. Use example in this package to test your BOINC configuration.
